{"tid":1577069,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"沒有私了，只有自衛！","createTime":"2019-09-17T13:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T15:09:32.000Z","uid":3177,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef988816809989b62c38f3838e7ab236b1119620","tid":1577069,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:43:51.000Z","msg":"私了唔應該成風氣<br />\n但面對廢老藍絲口講幾句就動手<br />\n絕對要搞清楚：自衛反擊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">沒有私了，只有自衛！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/594KYQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F594KYQj.jpg&h=7962aed2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"74f5af4fd74981020fa8b5a226f6df7741ecd8f6","tid":1577069,"uid":82993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T13:45:08.000Z","msg":"呢筆債，佢哋一定要還。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1576589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1576589</a>"},{"pid":"187fc6d5a17a0b7424ab6e609fb0d373cf88d587","tid":1577069,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},{"pid":"d8f8ae6b1ed02fbe79a108b5f3c68c642e2a39b5","tid":1577069,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:39:30.000Z","msg":"pushhhhh"},{"pid":"aae878dae101b975ca6ca556ea39a06b9c968c2b","tid":1577069,"uid":27814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:40:06.000Z","msg":"【數據分折，重溫 ！】想自殺？想重刷首抽？入黎睇睇先！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7853b1958b9aeead9226f620eec2ff676485bbb0","tid":1577069,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3jvagM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3jvagM.jpg&h=5676d08c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2f98fe782b115f7052a5d129eb5425a056d1690","tid":1577069,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:47:34.000Z","msg":"《叔敖斬蛇．豈是私了》<br />\n<br />\n春秋時期，有個名叫孫叔敖的小孩。有天，他外出玩耍後竟哭著回家，母親驚問何故。原來，叔敖見到了雙頭蛇。<br />\n<br />\n古人相信雙頭蛇乃不祥妖物，萬一不幸看見了，要死於非命的。小叔敖想到母親將要白頭人送黑頭人，就不禁哭了。母親追問「今蛇安在？」叔敖答曰：「我恐後人見之，故殺而埋之。」<br />\n<br />\n母親見孩兒高義，大為欣慰。孫叔敖也當然沒死，後來拜相於楚國，成為一代良相。「叔敖斬蛇」大仁大義的故事流芳後世，傳為美談。<br />\n<br />\n雙頭蛇，是很危險的 &mdash;&mdash; 按道理，不幸碰見的話當然是應該拔足而逃。小叔敖卻留下來「殺而埋之」，明顯不是為了自己，卻是為了保護別人。畢竟雙頭蛇在元朗、北角、荃灣都已經發動過恐襲。要是放蛇歸山，悲劇又會重演，受害者肯定越來越多。<br />\n<br />\n但打雙頭蛇，也是很危險的 &mdash;&mdash; 要知道，打蛇的後果可能相當嚴重：妖蛇兇暴，空羣而出，且手持利刃，打蛇者輕則被咬、重則喪命，此其一；其次，要是僥倖全身而退，母親卻可能會反過來「遣責暴力」而跟自己割蓆；再者，用來打蛇的餐刀也有可能被視為「攻擊性武器」，甚或招來勾結妖蛇的衙差濫捕，後果堪虞。但電光火石之間，叔敖想到的卻只有「我恐後人見之」的正義感，都顧不得那麼多危險了。<br />\n<br />\n由此可見，「叔敖斬蛇」是捨己為人的義舉，豈能稱之為「私了」？<br />\n<br />\n（當然，打蛇本應是衙差職責。然而衙差卻玩忽職守，勾結妖蛇。結果妖蛇橫行，害人無數，於是平民百姓只好勉力自救了。）<br />\n<br />\n#核爆都唔割<br />\n#願榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/664326578/posts/10157750394976579?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F664326578%2Fposts%2F10157750394976579%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5IpBSCas1SUWCM4mOsPk5ns%3D&h=3d544bfb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/664326578/posts/10157750394976579?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"8cda1c7b8e53b57c54df40d74599943cffd7f5aa","tid":1577069,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"187fc6d5a17a0b7424ab6e609fb0d373cf88d587","tid":1577069,"uid":3177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:05:19.000Z","msg":"pushhhh"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T14:50:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-help-hong-kong-citizens-bring-back-our-freedom-hong-kong-government-ignoring-our-voice-2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-help-hong-kong-citizens-bring-back-our-freedom-hong-kong-government-ignoring-our-voice-2&d=RXc9